# SmartPockets

Read AGENTS.md for full project context including architecture, patterns, and security requirements.

## Quick Rules

- Package manager: bun (pinned to 1.1.42)
- UI: UntitledUI components only (never create custom duplicates)
- Backend: Convex-first (no Next.js API routes)
- Imports: query/mutation from ./functions, NOT ./_generated/server
- Auth: Always derive userId from ctx.viewerX(), never from args
- Commits: Atomic, conventional format, one logical change each

## File Paths

- App code: apps/app/src/
- Convex backend: packages/backend/convex/
- UI components: packages/ui/src/
- Email templates: packages/email/emails/

## Do Not

- Use export const dynamic = "force-dynamic"
- Accept userId from function arguments
- Create components that duplicate UntitledUI
- Mutate edge-traversed entities (fetch writable via ctx.table().getX())
